Package: VcfAssociation
Title: Integrated VCF-Phenotype Association Analysis with Visualizations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("X Li", "xiaof.li@utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: Integrates VCF reading/annotation, association tests (GWAS/single-variant/gene-level), and visualizations (Manhattan/forest plots) for VCF/phenotype data (A3 Q1-2). Unique: one-step workflow reducing multi-package switching vs vcfR/qqman/VariantAnnotation (Q3). Assumptions: standard VCF/QC passed, matching IDs, sufficient sample size, covariates control stratification (Q5). Developed with R 4.3.0 on macOS.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
